<P>
   CONSTRUCTION-MANAGER (New York) _ Randy Polumbo is not an
interior decorator. Or an architect. Or a general contractor. In a
way, he is all of them _ the owner's eyes and ears on the job. He
is one of a relatively new breed of home improvement specialists: a
construction manager. By Tracie Rozhon.
