   OFFICE-CUBICLES (Undated) _ Anyone who works in a cubicle knows
that its shroudlike isolation bears no resemblance to real privacy.
But it may come as a surprise that the people who design today's
office systems agree that cubicles are long overdue for a makeover.
By Julie Iovine.
</P>
