</P>
<P>
   COMPUTERS-COLUMN (Undated) _ At last, an international standard
for 56-kilobit modems is in place. By Hiawatha Bray.
</P>
<P>
   COMPUTERS- (Undated) _ A cellular phone's address book can be
hard to use. Now manufacturers have given users a way to edit them
using a personal computer. By Simson Garfinkle.
</P>
