<P>
   PHILIPPINES-AIRLINES (Hong Kong) _ What happens to the
Philippines without its national airline. By Mark Landler.
</P>
<P>
   NISSON-BUILDING (Tokyo) _ Nissan Motor sells its headquarters
building in Tokyo for $107 million, taking another small step to
reduce its mammoth debts. By Stephanie Strom.
</P>
