<P>
   TRAVEL-WEBSITES-COX _ Most travelers aren't satisfied to merely
travel _ they want to foist their photographs and memories upon
their family, friends and any other poor saps they can take
hostage. But just as jet travel has opened up the world, the
Internet is allowing vacationers to air their exploits in front of
