<P>
   STATE-STREET-AURORA-BLOOM (Boston) _ State Street Research
Aurora Fund is set to join a growing list of small-company stock
mutual funds that are reopening to new investors amid expectations
the bear market for these stocks may be nearing an end. By Tim
Quinson.
</P>
<P>
   INVEST-OPIC-FUNDS-NYT (Undated) _ As most investors have watched
their holdings in the developing world _ from Asia to Latin America
to Russia _ evaporate over the last year, one group of politically
favored financiers has been able to look on more calmly. These are
investors who have put $3 billion into venture funds guaranteed by
the Overseas Private Investment Corp., a little-known government
agency that mixes private venture capital techniques with foreign
policy initiatives to plant capitalism in far-flung spots. By
Leslie Wayne. Graphic.
