 &HT;    COX NEWS SERVICE FRIDAY BUSINESS BUDGET
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   These business stories for release Friday, September 25, 1998,
are moving today to clients of the New York Times News Service.
</P>
<P>
