<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-24 17:21 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2797 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-EXECUTIVE-HOMICIDES-H     09-24 0841
