<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-EXECUTIVE-HOMICIDES-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
POLICE SAY TETRIS PARTNER KILLED FAMILY, SELF 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDs: Filed in national, ``a,'' and financial, ``f,'' categories)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By MATT BEER and JACOB FRIES  
 c.1998 San Francisco Examiner  
<TEXT>
<P>
