<HEADER>
A3105 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-BRAZIL-AUTO     09-24 0034
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-BRAZIL-AUTOS-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   BRAZIL-AUTOS (Taubate, Brazil) will not move in tonight's New
York Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, Sept. 24. &QL;
