   &UR; WHO SAID WHAT &LR;
</P>
<P>
   ``Making these horror movies isn't as easy as it might look.
You're trying to act, and there's all these damn puppeteers
crawling around under your feet.''
</P>
<P>
   _ Jennifer Tilly, who stars in the forthcoming movie ``Bride of
Chucky,'' in TV Guide Online.
</P>
