<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-24 21:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3305 &Cx1f; ttd-z
r f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BRODERBUND-SFCHRON &LR;      09-24 1009
