9-24 -- Mark Allemond, 11, displays a platter of crawfish served at
McGee's Landing. The restaurant is situated on stilts over the
Atchafalaya Basin, where tons of crawfish and other Cajun seafood
favorites are caught each year. (Syd Kearney/Houston Chronicle
Photo)
